latestIgtvVideos.title: My trip at Villa 30, Lonavla!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sharing a small glimpse of my staycation at Villa30! @redstonevillas 
Also mentioning all the safety measures taken by the staff! 

In response to current circumstances surrounding the COVID-19 pandemic, Redstone Villa has implemented a variety of new protocols and elevated practices, keeping with their high standards of cleanliness and luxury service. They ensured mandatory screening of body temperature upon arrival for all guests. 
Guests were also required to show their Arogya Setu App prior to entering the villa.
Every villa is thoroughly cleaned and disinfected prior to our arrival.
Food premises - Daily deep cleaning of operational kitchens was ensured using detergent scrubbing, steam pressure jets and sanitizing.
